creator: Microfun Limited
descriptionHtml:
There are everything you need to tide you through a monotonous day in Jellipop Match!

Adorable sugary-sweet graphics, exhilaratingly smooth controls, fascinating levels, an evil witch to defeat, and more. You’ll find yourself rebuilding heaps of cute shops of your dreams: milk tea shop, patisserie, candy store, flower shop, bookstore, cafe bar, fast food restaurant, toy store, bakery, chocolatier... lots of sweet, sweet businesses which you can design to your heart’s content! This lovingly crafted game is sure to bring you endless entertainment as you renovate buildings and enjoy the charming match-three world.

You’ve inherited an adorable town named Jelly Town in Jellipop Match, which used to be a prosperous town before being destroyed by evil witches. As the heir to this town, your residents: Lily, Austin, Zoe and etc. need you bring the town back to its former prosperous!

Show off your designer skill by restoring and decorating your Jelly Town with your new friends, beat a variety of exciting match-3 levels, explore the hidden secrets of the stories, unlock tons of stylish furniture and operate your shops with your friends in your town.

Embark on Jellipop Match adventure，Own your dream town for free！

The game features：
💌Entertaining gameplay：Match & swap，restore and decorate your own town；The magical sweets in Jelly Town are all pitching in to help take out the evil witch.Join forces with cute elephant-shaped jellies hidden under crystal sugar, explosive cat-paw marshmallows, and magical vortexes capable of conjuring even more magical jellies. With their aid, you’ll defeat the terrible witch for sure!
💌Thousands of levels with different elements：biscuit，magic soda cans，cream，wooden board，vine，wooden blocks，snowman；The game boasts over 1,500 carefully designed and non-repetitive levels, where you may collect a variety of delicious desserts and defeat the evil witch. You can also try out the day/night and green elves modes and immerse yourself in hours upon hours of jelly-matching fun!
💌A thriving town that belongs to you：discover more secrets as you own more shops.
💌Decorate different shops in your Jelly Town：Explore the meticulously hand-drawn mall and spot remnants of the previously prosperous Jelly Town. You’ll even get to design stores and select furniture as you rebuild the ruined mall! Each piece of furniture comes with at least 3 styles to choose from, ensuring that your creations will never look anything like your friends’!
💌Lots of characters in-game you can make friends with；you will always have Bingo at their side throughout the entire journey, but the more the merrier, right? Meet cute twin-tailed Alicia, sharp-tongued Bella, and adorably muddled Becky. What hilarious stories will these lively characters bring? Find out while you rebuild the town!
💌Varies of limited-time events and fascinating stories；Besides defeating the witch in mind-boggling levels, players may participate in lots of cool events. Venture into the toy castle with a day & night mode, try your luck at the claw machine, and even explore the creepy Halloween cemetery. Tons of other events await. Join and you’ll receive outrageous abilities that’ll be super helpful for clearing main storyline levels!

Last but not least, we would like to thank our loyal players for your support!

👉Love Jellipop Match？Learn more about this puzzle game！
Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/JellipopMatch/
Support team：jellipopmatch_service@microfun.com

Download this best match-3 puzzle game，enjoy the funnest cartoon puzzle journey！

❤Most importantly, a big THANK YOU to everyone who has played Jellipop Match!❤
